abstract: Former Gov. Ted Strickland of Ohio, a Democrat, is planning to challenge Senator Rob Portman, a Republican, next year, people familiar with Mr. Strickland’s plans said Tuesday.

headline.main: Ted Strickland to Seek to Unseat Senator Rob Portman in Ohio
